0.4.0:
* Remove implicit dependency on libm
* Fix l10n (bgo#652399)
* Rendering improvements (bgo#652684)
* Port to GtkApplication and GMenu (bgo#676601, bgo#676602)
* Use yelp-tools instead of gnome-doc-utils (Oliver Propst, bgo#683623)
* Translations:
** de (Mario Blättermann)
** el (Tom Tryfonidis)
** en_GB (Philip Withnall)
