0.3.0:
* Port to GTK+ 3
* Add timing support (bgo#575897)
* Improve the appearance of the game considerably
* Update the documentation and relicence it to cc-by-sa 3.0 (from GFDL 1.2)
* Translations:
** cs (Marek Černocký)
** da (Joe Hansen)
** de (Mario Blättermann)
